    - [Config] arm64: FTBFS, disable BCM_VC_CMA
    - [Config] arm64: FTBFS, disable BCM2708_VCHIQ
    - [Config] arm64: FTBFS, disable USB_DWCOTG
    - fix FTBFS rtl8192cu
    - arm64: fails booting when KGDB_SERIAL_CONSOLE=y, disable it

